content: Hi, the host said to get back on the zoom call at 2:50 for the wrap up, I am trying to connect but Iâ€™m still waiting to be let in the room. Can someone let me into the call?

I canâ€™t remember what the script said exactly, but a lot of it was very wordy so I trimmed some down because I could tell people didnâ€™t want to be on the phone too long.

Hi, thank you for sharing your experience (and apologies for not answering your parking question earlier) and your feedback! As to the script, it often can be super clunky so you did the right thing in cutting it down, which you are 100% welcome to do! And yeah, the dialer is a lot slower when there's not a ton of people making calls.
